txt.en: 'Are you looking to be welcomed into the inner circle of the Dunlendings of Dunland? I can help you with that and make you a \qKindred\q of the Dunlendings of Dunland.\n\n'If this sounds good to you, speak to me again!'
'Alright, soon you will be Kindred of the Dunlendings of Dunland. Ready?'
By completing this quest, you will be considered Kindred of the Dunlendings of Dunland.
